title: Making a Killing: The Untold Story of Psychotropic Drugging
description: Making a Killing - The Untold Story of Psychotropic Drugging (2008) Documentary.mp4 - 1h 34min 42s 720 x 480 https://extraimage.net/images/2018/09/16/1f1eab49717fc4dbbde667d2f548f5e5.jpg Psychotropic drugs. It's the story of big money-drugs that fuel a $330 billion psychiatric industry, without a single cure. The cost in human terms is even greater-these drugs now kill an estimated 42,000 people every year. And the death count keeps rising. Containing more than 175 interviews with lawyers, mental health experts, the families of victims and the survivors themselves, this riveting documentary rips the mask off psychotropic drugging and exposes a brutal but well-entrenched money-making machine.
